# ClampingAddable - Protocol for types that support clamping addition (+^)
module Core

### Defines the protocol `ClampingAddable`.
protocol ClampingAddable
  ### Implements the wired routine behavior for this value.
  ### :param you: The other value to compare against.
  ### :returns: The resulting `Me` value.
  @readonly
  routine Me.$add_clamp(you: Me) -> Me
